<h3><strong>Geography</strong></h3>
Kebumen is located near the Indian Ocean, it is also called Samudera Indonesia . The city is bisected by the Kali Lukulo (Lukulo River). It lies near three major roads, Jalan Pahlawan, Jalan HM. Sarbini and Jalan Ronggowarsito. Its geographic location is 7Â°40â€²33.4â€³S 109Â°39â€²50.6â€³E.

